description: Straight from the heartland, studly Trent Diesel is brand new to NK. Trent is very athletic and he has MMA background. With the NK record of 3-1, DJ is ready to add another notch on his belt. He's counting on Trent's inexperience with NK style. DJ strategy is to wear out Trent in the first round with his wrestling holds and sexually humiliates him in the sex round.
title: Trent Diesel vs DJ
